title: Scrapheap Challenge - 11x01 - Chariot Jousting.avi
description:
Dick Strawbridge hosts the new season of Scrapheap Challenge (aka JunkYard Wars)

Dicks' team "Dicks Diamonds" consists of regulars Dick Strawbridge, Jim Milner & guest Nikki Woolmore.

In this episode, three teams "The Scrappy Wacky Doodaas", "The Showmans" and "The Three Fallers", must build motorized jousting machines.

The winner out of the three teams gets the opportunity to take on "Dicks Diamonds" in the final and allowing them to compete in future challenges. 

Please help me seed & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

I'm adding one episode a day Mon - Fri as they air on ABC2 digital TV here in Australia. (We're getting them before the UK)
